      "street": "a) Afghanistan/Pakistan border area (previous location) b) Khan-Shaykhun, Syrian Arab Republic (53 km south of Idlib, location as of Mar. 2018) c) Idlib Aleppo and Khama, Syrian Arab Republic (operation zone) d) Faryab, Badghis and Jawzjan Provinces, Afghanistan",
      "country": "Afghanistan"
